{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"1ee38394-52d8-4c21-91ef-5672dbc5155c","content":"Here's the setup:\n\n**AppShell.xaml**\n```xml\n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<Shell x:Class=\"YourApp.AppShell\"\n       xmlns=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/dotnet/2021/maui\"\n       xmlns:x=\"http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2009/xaml\"\n       xmlns:views=\"clr-namespace:YourApp.Views\"\n       FlyoutBehavior=\"Flyout\">\n\n    <!-- Dashboard (single page) -->\n    <FlyoutItem Title=\"Dashboard\" Icon=\"dashboard.png\">\n        <ShellContent ContentTemplate=\"{DataTemplate views:DashboardPage}\" />\n    </FlyoutItem>\n\n    <!-- Products (two tabs) -->\n    <FlyoutItem Title=\"Products\" Icon=\"products.png\">\n        <Tab Title=\"Active\">\n            <ShellContent ContentTemplate=\"{DataTemplate views:ActiveProductsPage}\" />\n        </Tab>\n        <Tab Title=\"Archived\">\n            <ShellContent ContentTemplate=\"{DataTemplate views:ArchivedProductsPage}\" />\n        </Tab>\n    </FlyoutItem>\n\n    <!-- Settings -->\n    <FlyoutItem Title=\"Settings\" Icon=\"settings.png\">\n        <ShellContent ContentTemplate=\"{DataTemplate views:SettingsPage}\" />\n    </FlyoutItem>\n\n</Shell>\n```\n\n**AppShell.xaml.cs** — register the detail route:\n```csharp\nnamespace YourApp;\n\npublic partial class AppShell : Shell\n{\n    public AppShell()\n    {\n        InitializeComponent();\n\n        // Register route for programmatic navigation\n        Routing.RegisterRoute(nameof(Views.ProductDetailsPage), typeof(Views.ProductDetailsPage));\n    }\n}\n```\n\n**Navigating to details** (e.g., from ActiveProductsPage):\n```csharp\nawait Shell.Current.GoToAsync($\"{nameof(ProductDetailsPage)}?id={product.Id}\");\n```\n\n**Receiving the parameter** in `ProductDetailsPage`:\n```csharp\n[QueryProperty(nameof(ProductId), \"id\")]\npublic partial class ProductDetailsPage : ContentPage\n{\n    public string ProductId { get; set; }\n}\n```\n\n**Key points:**\n- `FlyoutItem` creates top-level flyout entries.\n- Wrapping `ShellContent` in multiple `<Tab>` elements within one `FlyoutItem` gives you the bottom tab bar for Products.\n- `Routing.RegisterRoute` is needed for pages that aren't in the visual hierarchy (like detail pages you push onto the navigation stack).","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"552c67ef-2caa-4421-a205-7884934730ed","outputTokens":634,"requestId":"9817:23A6C6:15F61F2:189DD15:6A052126"},"id":"a715eeaa-5002-4ca3-af1a-7263b6e7f3b8","timestamp":"2026-05-14T01:11:12.945Z","parentId":"89128035-8bc1-4647-9547-f94a03d5fe42"}
